# Persisted runtime data (DATA_DIR). In production these live on the Railway
# volume (/app/data); locally DATA_DIR defaults to the repo dir, so the server
# and --selftest write them here. Never commit them — names.json maps
# designations to wallet addresses, reports.json holds visitor reports, etc.
